  "title": "Sora 2 深夜来袭，OpenAI 直接推出 App，视频 ChatGPT 时刻到了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2650993618&idx=1&sn=6f991bbb004383a7bcc5b922af422c01",
  "date": "2025-09-30 23:47:00",
